ces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fde8d15762b7e2bf058c7769cb9c9e86b8f4ef","tid":2308623,"uid":231177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08558fa9925a9a32d687b7a0aff5815a3f1b85cb","tid":2308623,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b85325d3f9475e23a6d54b6c5013458a8f6f8267","tid":2308623,"uid":169895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201202/JBNZDV7FRRGVXP5WPEQ3XAHLV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201202%2FJBNZDV7FRRGVXP5WPEQ3XAHLV4%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=fd60a1bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201202%2FJBNZDV7FRRGVXP5WPEQ3XAHLV4%2F&h=4ad04751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201202/JBNZDV7FRRGVXP5WPEQ3XAHLV4/</a> <br />\n<br />\n落選港姐廖慧儀前男友疑情困 油麻地墮樓身亡<br />\n<br />\n油麻地文匯街1號文華樓，早上6時許，一名男子從大廈高處墮下，發出一聲隆然巨響，倒卧路面行車線上，吐血昏迷不醒，街坊見狀報警。救護員趕至現場，將傷者送往廣華醫院搶救，惟終告不治，現場遺下一灘血迹，警員封鎖附近一帶，並派員上樓進行調查，初步相信死者從天台跳下，警方於現場沒有撿獲遺書。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓張27歲，《蘋果》發現他在墮樓前半小時，在其IG留言尋死，用英文寫：Thank you for everyone who have been supporting throughout my journey.Goodbye.Please forgive me for doing this.Been suffering for 2 months both mentally and physically.Just couldn&rsquo;t take it any longer.Sorry（感謝所有在我人生旅途上一直給予的支持。再見。請原諒我。在精神和身體上遭受了2個月的苦難，再也忍受不了。）<br />\n<br />\n而同一個IG帳號，於今年10月31日發帖稱難忘舊愛廖慧儀。廖慧儀正是今屆落選港姐，張在IG說：「同你一齊呢一年半，大大小小傷心既（嘅）事我都陪你經歷過&hellip;點解要選擇因為1d小問題而狠心離開我，係咪因為入左娛樂圈&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n死者妹妹於早上11時40分在IG發帖說：「哥哥已經不在了，感謝你們的擔心，未來會有設靈，會再通知」。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"條女咁講算唔算blame the victim，怪返死者咁小事就尋死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"睇清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條女10月31 post架"}]}